summary: A nordic dungeon home near riverwood, work in progress; will gradually update to become a full quest.
descriptionHtml:
A nordic dungeon home near riverwood, work in progress; will gradually update to become a full quest for the home and followers. i created this to learn the creation kit and as i become better at using it, this mod will develop.

Should work with the NMM.

At the moment it is a solely a player home with everything you would expect, a bedroom, a crafting room, an equipment room and a living room. It is fully furnished with clutter and a fully working navmesh.

The exterior is now working as it should, and i have left the overpowered weapons in for now. 
Ive also added a few sets of armour and weapons around the place and changed the lighting(but im still not happy with the way it looks, so it will be updated).

Im uploading this for feedback and suggestions, so let me know what you think.

thanks
